algae still in water- sunny- light breeze
Sunny- calm- some algae in water
Harvester was in use at time of sample
Harvester was in use. Calm day- few boats.
partly cloudy. Windy. No boats. Harvester on lake.
Sunny with fluffy clouds- lake calm with no other boats.
sunny with few clouds- no other boats lake calm.  Lake weeds down.. due to cold spring
Mostly cloudy- lake calm.  Air temp mid 50's- no other boats.
sunny with fluffy clouds- no other boats- calm water
Clear sunny day.  Water calm. Clear sunny day.  Water calm.
Partly cloudy- slight wind- 1/2 inch rain June 21
Calm water- partly sunny- many floating islands of weeds.  Most of the lake's surface.

Slight wind. Partly sunny.  Many floating islands of weeds- most of lake surface. Slight wind. Partly sunny.  Many floating islands of weeds- most of lake surface. Slight wind. Partly sunny.  Many floating weed patches (should be harvested).
Partly Sunny - Lake calm and beautiful
Partly sunny- lake calm + beautiful 13' deep hole test site
Sunny clear day- slight wind- little chop on surface sunny- clear day- slight wind- little chop on water surface
Partly cloudy - slight ripple on water partly cloudy- slight ripple out on the water Partly cloudy - slight ripple on the water
clear and sunny (no clouds) slight ripple on the water clear and sunny (no clouds)- slight ripple on the water
clear and sunny (little clouds) water is calm- some floaters - harvestor out cutting
Partly Cloudy- Water choppy- no floating weeds- water appears clear- weed harvestor in service
calm sunny day- the lake looks great
Partly cloudy- fair calm- water high and clear- some weeds hitting surface
weed harvester on lake- partly cloudy- calm day- many weeds washing ashore/north bay and northeast shore
lake not as clear- water brown- no weeds hitting surface- lake looks good
Water clear and very good - no visible growing weed even near shore
Partly cloudy and windy- lake clear- weed harvester on the lake today
Cloudy day- weed harvester on lake today- no visible weeds hitting surface in boating area
Heavy rain the night before test- lake a little cloudy- otherwise lake looks great
Cool- windy morning. Lake looks good- no weeds showing on surface
Weather has been relatively cool- low 50's for three or four days- clear sky and windy- lake looks good
Beautiful day. No clouds- slight wind. Lake water looks great. Beautiful day- no clouds- slight wind- lake water looks great.
Partly cloudy slight breeze. Lake looks beautiful.
Weed harvester on lake- algae present on shores- otherwise lake looks good
Water murky- took photo to send to DNR
Clear sunny day. Lake level up and no weeds hitting surface.
Clear sunny day. Lake level up and no weeds seen hitting surface.
Sunny day- no weeds on surface.
Lake in very good shape- clear sunny day.
Low weeds. Ice out April 27- 2019. Water good condition for this time of year.
Weeds off bottom 2 feet. No weeds on surface. Muck stirred up in water.
weeds near surface. Some floating weeds. Muck stirred up in water.
Entire north bay weeds to surface. Some floating weeds. Muck stirred up in water.
No test in May because of Covid. Water good condition for this time of year.
